programme.desc: An acclaimed black pianist hires a white man to be his driver and bodyguard for his tour of the Jim Crow south, and as they set out for the long trip they realize that they have nothing in common, but as the trip goes on they forge a strong bond.

programme.title: Dark Waters
programme.desc: An attorney risks his career and family when he uncovers a dark secret that connects unexplained deaths to one of the world's largest corporations.

programme.title: Secret Window
programme.desc: Mort Rainey, a writer just coming off of a troublesome divorce with his ex-wife, Amy, finds himself stalked at his remote lake house by a psychotic stranger who claims Mort stole his best story idea.

programme.title: The End of the Tour
programme.desc: Based on true events, 'Rolling Stone' magazine reporter David Lipsky sets out to interview best-selling author David Foster Wallace following the release of his hit novel "Infinite Jest," and the two quickly develop a bond.

programme.title: Reality Bites
programme.desc: Four friends face the promise and pitfalls of life in the 1990s when they share a house.

programme.title: First Reformed
programme.desc: A pastor at a small rural church struggles with guilt over his son's death, an unidentified illness and his dwindling congregation, but when a pregnant woman asks him to help save her disturbed husband he discovers a way to solve all of his problems.

programme.title: True History of the Kelly Gang
programme.desc: Notorious 19th century outlaw Ned Kelly recounts the tales of his life, from his hardscrabble upbringing to his gang's attempts to outrun the authorities.

programme.title: Trespass Against Us
programme.desc: After an elaborate heist goes south, a reluctant criminal must find a way to escape from the clutches of his fierce outlaw father and the encroaching police.

programme.title: Burden
programme.desc: An idealistic Reverend is tossed in the middle of racial tensions when a museum celebrating the Ku Klux Klan opens in a South Carolina town.

programme.title: Blow Out
programme.desc: A man is in danger when he records evidence that proves an 'accident' was really murder.

programme.title: Ginger & Rosa
programme.desc: A lifelong friendship between two teenage girls Ginger and Rosa, growing up in 1960s London is shattered by one pivotal event.

programme.title: Laggies
programme.desc: A 28-year-old woman with no motivation or career prospects befriends a 16-year-old girl after fleeing her boyfriend's marriage proposal. Needing a break from her life, she hides out for a week spending time with the high schooler and her single dad.

programme.title: Legally Blonde
programme.desc: When a fashion-driven sorority girl is dumped by her boyfriend, she decides to follow him to law school. Harvard doesn't know what to do when Elle and her dog take the Ivy League institution by storm.

programme.title: Hot Summer Nights
programme.desc: A teen sent to stay with his aunt in Cape Cod for the summer struggles to fit in, but after a chance encounter with a small-time drug dealer he begins selling drugs to other teens, using his brains to help grow his new partner's illicit operation.

programme.title: Red
programme.desc: A retired black-ops agent brings his old team back together in an attempt to uncover the assailants that attacked him in his home.

programme.title: Hollywoodland
programme.desc: Based on the life of actor George Reeves, who played 'Superman' on TV in the 1950's and who died under mysterious circumstances in 1959.

programme.title: Collide
programme.desc: In order to pay for his girlfriend's kidney transplant, an American backpacker is sent on a heist. When it goes wrong, the mob boss demands his death and kidnaps his girlfriend. He must elude his pursuers in a high-speed chase on the German autobahn.

programme.title: Miami Vice
programme.desc: Two vice squad agents work undercover transporting drugs for a Columbian drug cartel while searching for evidence they murdered the wife of an informant. Complicating matters is the Aryan Brotherhood, who supply arms to the cartel in exchange for drugs.

programme.title: Red
programme.desc: A retired black-ops agent brings his old team back together in an attempt to uncover the assailants that attacked him in his home.

programme.title: The Samaritan
programme.desc: An ex-con meets a young woman and things are looking good, but his past comes back to haunt them.
